</spec>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000013B501PX_01_0004" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000010500000">
<ptxt>INSPECT OIL PUMP DRIVE GEAR ROTATION</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C191445" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that the drive gear rotates smoothly.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the oil pump from the torque converter.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
